{"word":"Eli","slug":"eli","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Eli</b> <a href=\"#/H5941\">H5941</a> <br/> High priest<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=1&verse=25'>1Sa 1:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=2&verse=11'>1Sa 2:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=2&verse=27'>1Ki 2:27</a><br/> Judge of Israel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=4&verse=18'>1Sa 4:18</a><br/> Misjudges and rebukes Hannah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=1&verse=14'>1Sa 1:14</a><br/> His benediction upon Hannah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=1&verse=18'>1Sa 1:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=2&verse=20'>1Sa 2:20</a><br/> Officiates when Samuel is presented at the tabernacle<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=1&verse=28'>1Sa 1:28</a><br/> Indulgent to his corrupt sons<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=2&verse=25'>1Sa 2:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=2&verse=29'>1Sa 2:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=3&verse=14'>1Sa 3:14</a><br/> His solicitude for the ark<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=4&verse=18'>1Sa 4:18</a><br/> Death of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=4&verse=18'>1Sa 4:18</a><br/> Prophecies of judgments upon his house<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=2&verse=36'>1Sa 2:36</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=3'>1Sa 3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=2&verse=27'>1Ki 2:27</a>"}]}